<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Resume Approved</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #333;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .email-header {
      background-color: #4caf50;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .email-header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    .email-body {
      padding: 20px 30px;
    }
    .email-body h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #4caf50;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .email-body p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #4caf50;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #45a049;
    }
    .email-footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #777;
    }
    .email-footer a {
      color: #4caf50;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>Resume Approved</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
      <h2>Dear {{candidateName}},</h2>
      <p>
        We are pleased to inform you that your resume for the <strong>{{jobTitle}}</strong> position at <strong>{{companyName}}</strong> has been <span style="color: #4caf50;">approved</span>.
      </p>
      <p>
        Please log in to your account to review the next steps in the application process.
      </p>
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{dashboardLink}}" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
      </div>
      <p>
        If you have any questions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@example.com">support@example.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>Thank you for choosing {{companyName}}!</p>
      <p>Â© {{currentYear}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
